                                    <component>java</component>
                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>2</watches>
                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="15250131" author="rdblue" created="Wed, 20 Apr 2016 15:52:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think this is a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1799&quot; title=&quot;java: GenericData.toString() mutates underlying ByteBuffer backed data&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AVRO-1799&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AVRO-1799&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, which was &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/avro/blame/master/lang/java/avro/src/main/java/org/apache/avro/generic/GenericData.java#L550&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;fixed&lt;/a&gt; and will be in the upcoming 1.8.1 release. Can you confirm that it looks like the same issue?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15251395" author="odidukh" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2016 06:49:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, it&apos;s the same issue.&lt;br/&gt;
Could you tell me when are you going to release 1.8.1 version?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15252166" author="rdblue" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2016 16:32:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;re discussing the 1.8.1 release on the mailing list and want to release in the new couple of weeks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
