                            <comment id="15252181" author="rdblue" created="Thu, 21 Apr 2016 16:46:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m adding &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1684&quot; title=&quot;Add date, time, and timestamp to specific object model classes&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;AVRO-1684&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;AVRO-1684&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. I&apos;ve seen quite a few requests for it.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
