&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mtth&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mtth&quot;&gt;Matthieu Monsch&lt;/a&gt;, can you add me as a maintainer for Avro on NPM? My username is rdblue.&lt;/p&gt;

